excerpt.rendered:
OCCASION ALERT

This Bull 50 E has been proudly owned by an ‘older’ couple since 2013. Having enjoyed and enjoyed the Queen Mary III for many years, they decided it was time for others to enjoy it. The aluminum sloop is 4.50 meters long and 1.80 meters wide. The draft is 40 centimeters and the headroom is 1.10 meters.

The Bull 50 E is equipped with:
  1. Full powder coating;
  2. Stainless steel finishing package;
  3. Flagpole with flag;
  4. Boarding post;
  5. Fenders;
  6. 2.5 KW – 235 Amp/h;
  7. Complete cushion set of Sunbrella with raised back cushions.

More information about the Bull 50 E model can be found here.

Is this the boat of your dreams? Please contact us!
